               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām “Miracles of Mary” (fols. 2ra-9va, 19rb-57rb)&#xD; I-1)
                     Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 2ra-6ra) &#xD; I-2)
                     Introductory exhortation (fols. 6ra-7va) &#xD; I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki
                     wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... “I worship Thee…” (fols. 7va-9va) &#xD; II) Taʾāmra Gabra
                     Manfas Qǝddus "Miracles of Gabra Manfas Qǝddus": 3 miracles (fols.
                     9va-11rb)&#xD; III) Taʾāmra Mikāʾel “Miracles of Michael”: 3 miracles (fols.
                     11rb-13va)&#xD; IV) Taʾāmra Giyorgis “Miracles of George”: 3 miracles (fols.
                     13va-14vb)&#xD; V) Taʾāmra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus”: 3 miracles (fols.
                     14vb-19rb)&#xD; I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām: 33 miracles (fols. 19rb-57rb [incipit fol.
                     21ra])&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1; colophon.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                     <locus target="#57rb">57rb</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘአጽሐፎ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ኃይለ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ አቡሁ፡ ቀሲስ፡
                     ክፍለ፡ ማርያም፡ ወእሙ፡ ሰበነ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ወጸሐፊሁ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖ፡ መድኀኒተ፡ ነፍስ፡ ወሥጋ፡
                     ዘወሀቦ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ መዓጔ፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ ውጉዞ፡ ይኩን፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ወበቃለ፡ ወአኒ፡
                     ውጉዞ፡ ለይኩን። The colophon mentions the name of the commissioner and donor priest
                     (qasis ) Ḫāyla Giyorgis, that of his father, priest Kǝfla Māryām, of his
                     mother, Säbänä Giyorgis, and that of the scribe, priest Takla Hāymānot. It
                     mentions also that the Ms. was donated to the church Giyorgis Mäʿagwe.
                  </colophon>
